      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>麟之趾，振振公子，于嗟麟兮。
麟之定，振振公姓，于嗟麟兮。
麟之角，振振公族，于嗟麟兮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The feet of the lin:—
The noble sons of our prince,
Ah! they are the lin!

The forehead of the lin:—
The noble grandsons of our prince,
Ah! they are the lin!

The horn of the lin:—
The noble kindred of our prince,
Ah! they are the lin!</seg>
      </tuv>
